msg.msgText: "{0}" is a {1} configuration object. Use either the "imaserver show" command, or the "imaserver list" command.For some composite objects, only one command is supported.

msgExplanation.p: The 'imaserver get' command is only use for singleton objects.

msgUserResponse.p: Use 'imaserver list' or 'imaserver show' command for the composite object. Use the help command for more details.
